whenever a phone is updated. The tech support and bug report people never 
get back to you. The app is useless unless you are ok waiting 5 mins in 
between each message. But it's 2018.... No type messaging should take this 
long. I really miss when you could check messages on the site or app 
without FB messenger app. That never had issues.

From my point of view it has extra useless features, and furthermore, is 
kinda difficult to take a look at someone's Facebook profile from this app 
(you need to do a lot of taps). But overall, it does what it is supposed to 
do, and video calls are pretty good.

onto the messenger platform. The messenger app is a communication app much 
like WhatsApp. Why is there a need to add intrusive ads to the app. 
Perfectly ruin a much good tool.
